793	### 坑3: Canvas Scaler导致的性能问题
794	
795	**现象：** UI元素位置计算异常、DrawCall增加
796	
797	**根因：**
798	```
799	Canvas Scaler: Scale With Screen Size
800	├─> 每帧计算缩放比例
801	├─> 所有RectTransform重新计算
802	└─> Layout System重新布局
803	```
804	
805	**解决方案：**
806	```csharp
807	// 固定分辨率缩放
808	public class FixedResolutionScaler : MonoBehaviour
809	{
810	    private const int ReferenceWidth = 1920;
811	    private const int ReferenceHeight = 1080;
812	
813	    private CanvasScaler scaler;
814	
815	    private void Awake()
816	    {
817	        scaler = GetComponent<CanvasScaler>();
818	        scaler.uiScaleMode = CanvasScaler.ScaleMode.ConstantPixelSize;
819	        scaler.scaleFactor = GetScaleFactor();
820	    }
821	
822	    private float GetScaleFactor()
823	    {
824	        float referenceRatio = (float)ReferenceWidth / ReferenceHeight;
825	        float screenRatio = (float)Screen.width / Screen.height;
826	
827	        if (screenRatio > referenceRatio)
828	        {
829	            // 宽屏，基于高度缩放
830	            return (float)Screen.height / ReferenceHeight;
831	        }
832	        else
833	        {
834	            // 窄屏，基于宽度缩放
835	            return (float)Screen.width / ReferenceWidth;
836	        }
837	    }
838	}
839	```
